+--------------+
|  SMS Bomber  |
+--------------+

This script was created out of boredom and to build on an inside joke. I am pretty sure that this is illegal to do to somebody, so, use at your own risk.

USAGE
------

Call the script and enter the information into the fields. As of right now, you must have a G-Mail account and the only supported carriers are AT&T, Verizon, T-Mobile, Sprint, and Virgin Mobile. If you need added functionality, the code is self-explanatory, or you can send an e-mail to d1zzy.lulz@gmail.com .



